message.content: The paper likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and intent classification. Other likely sub-categories could include "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to NLP and LSTM architectures. "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) and "cs.CV" (Computer Vision) are less likely as they are not directly related to the problem of intent classification in question answering.
